  Step 2: [iot] none — Filter the list to find one representative healthy unit (T-005) and one degraded unit (T-013) (depends on steps [1])
  Step 3: [iot] list_sensors — Surface the available sensor channels for the healthy unit (T-005) (depends on steps [2])
  Step 4: [iot] list_sensors — Surface the available sensor channels for the degraded unit (T-013) (depends on steps [2])
  Step 5: [iot] get_sensor_readings — Get recent telemetry samples for each sensor channel of the healthy unit (T-005) (depends on steps [3])
